<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:14:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>香港法院驳回结束黎智英审判的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-end-jimmy-lai-trial-2024-07-25/</link><description>香港一家法院周四驳回了法律团队对被监禁的民主党人黎智英终止国家安全审判的请求，称检察官有足够的表面证据让审判继续进行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:52:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-end-jimmy-lai-trial-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>科技股暴跌打击亚洲股市，日元升至 2-1/2 个月高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-25/</link><description>由于全球科技股暴跌，投资者纷纷转向风险较低的资产，包括短期债券、日元和瑞士法郎，亚洲股市周四遭受重创。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:36:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>央行意外开展中期贷款操作并下调利率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-central-bank-unexpectedly-conducts-medium-term-loan-operation-cuts-2024-07-25/</link><description>继本周早些时候一系列降息之后，中国央行周四出人意料地进行了中期借贷便利（MLF）操作并下调了利率。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:45:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-central-bank-unexpectedly-conducts-medium-term-loan-operation-cuts-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>由于对中国需求疲软和中东停火谈判的担忧，油价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-ease-concerns-over-weak-china-demand-mideast-ceasefire-talks-2024-07-25/</link><description>由于对全球最大原油进口国中国需求疲软的担忧以及对中东即将达成停火协议的预期克服了美国库存减少后前一交易日的涨幅，油价周四下跌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:35:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-ease-concerns-over-weak-china-demand-mideast-ceasefire-talks-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>套利交易平仓，日元上涨，风险情绪受到打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-rises-carry-trades-unwind-risk-sentiment-takes-hit-2024-07-25/</link><description>周四，在下周日本央行(BOJ)政策会议之前，套利交易平仓，以及大型成长型股票的轮换普遍抑制了风险偏好，并提供了一些避险买盘，日元因此获得支撑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:05:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-rises-carry-trades-unwind-risk-sentiment-takes-hit-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>美军拦截俄罗斯和中国飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-intercepts-russian-chinese-aircraft-2024-07-25/</link><description>美国军方周三表示，拦截了在阿拉斯加防空识别区飞行的两架俄罗斯和两架中国军用飞机，尽管它们仍在国际空域。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:41:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-intercepts-russian-chinese-aircraft-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>台风“嘉美”横扫台湾，造成两人死亡，正前往中国海岸</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/typhoon-gaemi-passes-over-taiwan-heads-chinese-coast-2024-07-25/</link><description>周四，台风“嘉美”横扫台湾北部，造成两人死亡、洪水泛滥、交通混乱，随后跨海进入中国大陆，预计将带来更多暴雨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/typhoon-gaemi-passes-over-taiwan-heads-chinese-coast-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国主要银行在降低贷款利率后降低存款利率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/major-chinese-banks-cut-deposit-rates-after-reduction-lending-rates-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国五家主要国有银行周四表示，将下调存款利率，几天前，中国下调基准贷款利率以提振陷入困境的经济，令市场感到意外。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/major-chinese-banks-cut-deposit-rates-after-reduction-lending-rates-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>专家称，中国的秘密航天飞机可能正在测试“双重用途”技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-secretive-spaceplane-likely-testing-dual-use-technology-experts-say-2024-07-25/</link><description>专家表示，中国的无人可重复使用航天器在火箭助推器顶部发射，降落在一个秘密军用机场，很可能是在测试技术，但也可用于操纵或回收卫星。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-secretive-spaceplane-likely-testing-dual-use-technology-experts-say-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：巨型海啸即将来临</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-07-24/</link><description>奥尔登·本特利 (Alden Bentley) 在纽约展望亚洲市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:49:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国告诉跨国公司台湾员工不要违法，没什么好害怕的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/dont-break-law-you-have-nothing-fear-china-tells-taiwan-staff-multinational-2024-07-24/</link><description>中国政府周三表示，在中国跨国公司的台湾员工只要不违法就没有什么可担心的，因为新的法律指导方针要求在极端情况下处决“顽固”分裂分子。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:06:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/dont-break-law-you-have-nothing-fear-china-tells-taiwan-staff-multinational-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>日经新闻报道本田将削减在中国的内燃机汽车产能</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automaker-honda-slash-gas-cars-production-capacity-china-nikkei-says-2024-07-24/</link><description>据《日经新闻》周四报道，汽车制造商本田汽车计划将内燃机汽车的产能削减三分之一，因为来自低价本土制造商的竞争加剧对日本汽车制造商的销售造成压力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 20:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automaker-honda-slash-gas-cars-production-capacity-china-nikkei-says-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>意大利总理梅洛尼本周将访华并提出贸易和投资议程</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/italys-meloni-visit-china-this-week-with-trade-investment-agenda-2024-07-24/</link><description>一位参与计划的人士告诉路透社，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼将于7月26日至31日访问中国，这是她上任以来的首次访问，旨在改善与中国的贸易。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 16:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/italys-meloni-visit-china-this-week-with-trade-investment-agenda-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国对帮助朝鲜的中国网络实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-imposes-sanctions-china-based-network-helping-north-korea-2024-07-24/</link><description>美国财政部表示，美国周三对一家帮助朝鲜发展弹道导弹和太空计划的中国网络实施制裁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:33:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-imposes-sanctions-china-based-network-helping-north-korea-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>奥的斯因中美建筑活动放缓下调年度销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/otis-cuts-annual-sales-view-slowdown-construction-activity-china-us-2024-07-24/</link><description>由于北美和中国对其新设备的需求疲软，电梯制造商奥的斯环球公司 (Otis Worldwide) 周三下调了 2024 年净销售额预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 12:08:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/otis-cuts-annual-sales-view-slowdown-construction-activity-china-us-2024-07-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>